These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-1::.
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, tomato, broccoli, radish
4 different pets are kept: rat, dog, rabbit, fish
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, car, bike, tram
1. the person driving the bike is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
2. the person driving the tram is the owner of the rat##1
3. the person eating broccoli is on the far left##1
4. the person eating lettuce is on the far right##1
5. the owner of the dog is between the person driving the bike and the person eating tomato##2
6. the person driving the car is the owner of the rabbit##1
7. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | broccoli | radish  | tomato | lettuce  |
| Pet         | fish    | dog  | rat       | rabbit     |
| Transport   | bike     | scooter | tram       | car |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, board-games, skydiving, writing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, musical, thriller
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, baseball, skiing, rowing
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is rowing is between the person watching thriller movies and the person who's hobby is writing##2
5. the person watching thriller movies is the person who's sport is baseball##1
6. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
7. the person watching musical movies is the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | board-games | puzzles    | writing  | skydiving |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller  | animation  | documentary   | musical    |
| Sport         | baseball | rowing | volleyball | skiing      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, hot-chocolate, coffee, juice
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, woodworking, singing, skydiving
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, r&b, jazz, ambient
1. the fan of r&b is between the fan of ambient and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the fan of classical##1
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
4. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left##1
6. the fan of classical is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
7. the fan of jazz is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | juice         | milk   | coffee    |
| Hobby         | woodworking | skydiving | puzzles | singing |
| Music-Genre   | jazz   | r&b        | ambient      | classical   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, french, chinese, pakistani
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, rowing, climbing, sailing
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, snowmobile, subway, trike
1. the person driving the subway is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the boat is between the person driving the trike and the pakistani##2
3. the chinese is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
4. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
5. the chinese is on the right of the brazilian##1
6. the person driving the trike is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person driving the snowmobile##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |   4    |
| Nationality   | pakistani        | french   | brazilian | chinese |
| Sport         | climbing | surfing | rowing    | sailing |
| Transport     | subway       | boat     | trike       | snowmobile    |

