.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, water, milk, sprite
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, camping, traveling, collecting
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, swimming, parkour, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is between the person drinking coffee and the person drinking water##2
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person drinking sprite##1
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
7. the person who's sport is lacrosse is between the person who's sport is parkour and the person who's hobby is cooking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |      3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | coffee | sprite      | water       | milk   |
| Hobby      | cooking   | camping  | collecting | traveling     |
| Sport      | swimming     | lacrosse | parkour        | cycling |

