.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-6::.
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, lime, broccoli, papaya
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, video-games, dancing, reading
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, golf, badminton, water-polo
1. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
2. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person eating lime##1
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's sport is badminton##2
6. the person eating lime is between the person eating blueberry and the person eating broccoli##2
7. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food    | broccoli | lime  | blueberry | papaya      |
| Hobby   | dancing  | reading  | drawing | video-games |
| Sport   | water-polo | lacrosse | golf | badminton     |

