.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-7::.
There 4 different types of food: kiwi, asparagus, mango, peach
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, horror, adventure, fantasy
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, cricket, baseball, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person watching horror movies##1
2. the person who's sport is baseball is the person watching musical movies##1
3. the person watching adventure movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
5. the person eating mango is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
6. the person eating asparagus is between the person watching horror movies and the person watching adventure movies##2
7. the person eating peach is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Food          | mango  | asparagus    | peach | kiwi  |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | fantasy       | horror        | musical    |
| Sport         | cricket | rowing | weightlifting  | baseball |

