.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, drawing, traveling, baking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, satire, mystery, adventure
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, turtle, goldfish, ferret
1. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the person watching satire movies is between the owner of the ferret and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
6. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | baking  | drawing | traveling | collecting |
| Movie-Genre   | horror  | adventure | satire   | mystery         |
| Pet           | guinea-pig | goldfish  | turtle   | ferret      |

