4. the person who's hobby is camping is the person eating kiwi##1
5. the person eating lime is on the right of the person eating pear##1
6. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far right##1
7. the person who's hobby is traveling is between the fan of pop and the person who's hobby is singing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
