1. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left##1
2. the person eating grapefruit is on the far left##1
3. the person eating blueberry is between the person eating eggplant and the person who's hobby is cooking##2
4. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
5. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far right##1
6. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
7. the person watching zombie movies is the person who's hobby is reading##1
8. the person watching sports movies is the person eating cherry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |   3    |    4    |
