.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, potato, broccoli, blueberry
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, collecting, drawing, hiking
4 different pets are kept: bird, goldfish, cat, turtle
1. the person eating potato is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
2. the owner of the cat is the person eating potato##1
3. the owner of the bird is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
4. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the owner of the bird and the person eating blueberry##2
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is the owner of the turtle##1
6. the person who's hobby is cooking is the owner of the goldfish##1
7. the person who's hobby is hiking is the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Food    | blueberry  | broccoli | asparagus | potato     |
| Hobby   | cooking | drawing   | hiking  | collecting    |
| Pet     | goldfish        | turtle       | bird      | cat |

