.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-12::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, lemonade, soy-milk, milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, rock-climbing, singing, collecting
4 different pets are kept: rat, cat, lizard, goldfish
1. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person drinking soy-milk##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##2
4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
6. the owner of the rat is on the far right##1
7. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | milk | soy-milk     | lemonade | cola       |
| Hobby      | singing  | collecting | chess  | rock-climbing |
| Pet        | goldfish  | cat      | lizard        | rat      |

