3. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is the owner of the hedgehog##1
5. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
6. the person drinking mirinda is the person who's hobby is dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |     3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | lemonade | mirinda  | iced-tea       | juice   |
| Hobby      | baking     | dancing | gardening | puzzles |
| Pet        | hedgehog        | dog | rat     | frog |

