.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-14::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, police-officer, doctor, videographer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, scientific, horror, drama
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, bike, helicopter, train
1. the person watching western movies is the person driving the train##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is the doctor##1
3. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the accountant##1
4. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person driving the train##1
5. the person driving the bike is between the person watching horror movies and the doctor##2
6. the person driving the train is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the bike is the videographer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Job           | police-officer | videographer | doctor    | accountant   |
| Movie-Genre   | horror      | scientific   | drama | western |
| Transport     | van     | bike       | helicopter        | train    |

