.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, juice, water, sprite
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, jazz, dubstep, reggae
There are 4 different nationalities: american, indonesian, australian, nigerian
1. the fan of ambient is the person drinking juice##1
2. the person drinking tea is between the person drinking water and the indonesian##2
3. the person drinking water is the fan of jazz##1
4. the person drinking water is between the fan of dubstep and the nigerian##2
5. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking water##1
6. the american is between the australian and the fan of reggae##2
7. the fan of ambient is the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Beverage      | juice | water | tea   | sprite |
| Music-Genre   | ambient  | jazz    | dubstep   | reggae     |
| Nationality   | nigerian  | australian | american | indonesian   |

