.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, almond-milk, juice, sprite
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, raspberry, garlic, mango
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, badminton, golf, sailing
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
2. the person eating garlic is between the person drinking sprite and the person who's sport is golf##2
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the far right##1
5. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
6. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
7. the person drinking juice is the person who's sport is handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate    | almond-milk | sprite           | juice |
| Food       | grapefruit | garlic    | raspberry          | mango   |
| Sport      | golf  | badminton   | sailing | handball  |

