2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person drinking water##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person watching fantasy movies and the person watching comedy movies##2
5. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
6. the owner of the fish is between the person drinking coffee and the owner of the lizard##2
7. the person watching action movies is the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage      | water | iced-tea | coffee     | mirinda   |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | action        | fantasy  | documentary  |
| Pet           | lizard      | fish         | ferret | pony |

