.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-20::.
There 4 different types of food: plum, raspberry, avocado, pumpkin
4 different pets are kept: lizard, pony, chinchilla, rabbit
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, ship, boat, snowmobile
1. the owner of the lizard is on the far left##1
2. the person eating plum is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
3. the person driving the ship is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
4. the person eating avocado is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the snowmobile is the owner of the rabbit##1
6. the owner of the pony is between the person eating pumpkin and the person driving the boat##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | pumpkin | raspberry | plum | avocado |
| Pet         | lizard       | pony     | chinchilla   | rabbit   |
| Transport   | taxi | ship | boat | snowmobile |

 